snippet.title: Warspace game trailer
snippet.description:
The main sale will take place on January 12 at 19:00 UTC. It will consist of two parts: Private Drop (for Premium Pass holders only: 800 premium packs + 1600 starter packs) and Public Drop (for the community: 2400 starter packs).

https://warspace.io/
